Most java games for Nokia 5800 will work perfect on SE Satio, but on some the black built in "touch screen button system" appears and all is ruined.

you can find symbian games on mobiles24.com

Turn off the virtual keys in app manager, it should work then as fullscreen:

Menu > Settings > Application manager > Installed apps > "Select touch game in 360x640" > Options > Suite setting > On-screen keyboard > OFF

Also, some games are not fullscreen, they only play in half a screen, it's just the way those games are
